  "id": "BIT-java-min-2025-6021",
  "summary": "Libxml2: integer overflow in xmlbuildqname() leads to stack buffer overflow in libxml2",
  "details": "A flaw was found in libxml2's xmlBuildQName function, where integer overflows in buffer size calculations can lead to a stack-based buffer overflow. This issue can result in memory corruption or a denial of service when processing crafted input.",
